.name
Stocks
.type
Financial Analysis
.short
Comprehensive stocks analysis program
.description
Demo version of a stocks analysis program.  Provides powerful
technical analysis using numerous studies including Candlesticks,
traditional bar charts, 3 moving averages, MACD, Stochastics,
Gann, TrendLines,%R, Average Volume and more.  It generates
buy/sell signals based on customizable trading rules and graphs
daily, weekly, and monthly charts using a simple ASCII data file
format compatable with CompuServe historical data.  Displays on
Workbench or Custom Public Screen.  Includes on-line AmigaGuide
help text. Binary only.
.version
3.02a
.author
James Philippou, Bug-Free Development
.restrictions
Demo version limited to supplied examples only.
.requirements
Requires OS2.0+
